<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,152,514]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
Mesotrochanter and middle femur lacking nodules, but with abundant dark hair; mesocoxae entirely covered with tuft-like setae (
<figureCitation box="[486,557,189,215]" captionStart="FIGURES 2 – 6" captionStartId="3.[151,273,1954,1978]" captionTargetBox="[241,1324,220,1928]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[205,1381,194,1933]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 2 – 6. Structural details of Martarega new species. 2 – 3, M. awa, 2 hemelytron of female, 3 male genital capsule; 4 – 6, M. lofoides, 4 hemelytron of female, 5 middle leg, omitted tarsus, 6 male genital capsule." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/197020/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
Fig. 
<number box="[541,557,189,215]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" value="5.0">5</number>
</figureCitation>
); all trochanters with a tuft of dark hair, near the coxae.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1436,152,514]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
Genital capsule and left paramere (
<figureCitation box="[619,694,226,252]" captionStart="FIGURES 2 – 6" captionStartId="3.[151,273,1954,1978]" captionTargetBox="[241,1324,220,1928]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[205,1381,194,1933]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 2 – 6. Structural details of Martarega new species. 2 – 3, M. awa, 2 hemelytron of female, 3 male genital capsule; 4 – 6, M. lofoides, 4 hemelytron of female, 5 middle leg, omitted tarsus, 6 male genital capsule." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/197020/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
Fig. 
<number box="[676,694,226,252]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" value="6.0">6</number>
</figureCitation>
). Female with a long spine characteristic on lateral margin of middle femur, close to point of joint with trochanter (
<figureCitation box="[774,839,264,290]" captionStart="FIGURES 2 – 6" captionStartId="3.[151,273,1954,1978]" captionTargetBox="[241,1324,220,1928]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[205,1381,194,1933]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 2 – 6. Structural details of Martarega new species. 2 – 3, M. awa, 2 hemelytron of female, 3 male genital capsule; 4 – 6, M. lofoides, 4 hemelytron of female, 5 middle leg, omitted tarsus, 6 male genital capsule." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/197020/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">
Fig 
<number box="[822,839,264,290]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" value="6.0">6</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
